<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Hidden Manuscript</title>
    <link href="/util.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>

<body>
{{>util/header}}

<section>
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; margin: 2rem 0 1rem 1rem; user-select: none;">
        Acoustics
    </h1>
</section>

<div class="layout" style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start;">
    <aside class="sidebar" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; margin-left: 1rem;">
        <label class="sidebar-button">
            <span class="checkbox">Archaeoacoustics</span>
        </label>
    </aside>

    <section class="main-content" style="
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin: 0 1.5rem 1rem 1.5rem;
        min-width: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
    ">
        <article class="yellow-box" style="width: auto; height: auto; max-width: 100%;">
            <p class="yellow-box-text">KSWN (Kannada SentiWordNet): Developing a Sentiment Lexicon for Kannada using Translation and Word Embedding Techniques</p>

            <div class="authors" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                <button>Rashmi Kariganuru Bheemarao1</button>
                <button>Hassan Sadashiva Guruprasad1</button>
                <button>Shambhavi Bangalore Ravi2</button>
            </div>

            <p style="font-weight: 100; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.2rem; user-select: none;">Published: 9 June 2025</p>
            <p style="font-weight: 100; font-size: 0.8rem">Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book...</p>
            <footer class="yellow-box-buttons" style="margin-top: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 0;">
                <button class="m3-button red-button" style="font-size: 0.8rem; width: fit-content; box-shadow: none; text-wrap: nowrap; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 1rem;">Delete permanently</button>
                <button class="m3-button outline-button" style="font-size: 0.8rem; width: fit-content; text-wrap: nowrap; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; background-color: white;">Restore</button>
            </footer>
        </article>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="overlay">
    <div class="dialog">
        <p>Permanently delete <b>KSWN (Kannada SentiWordNet): Developing a Sentiment Lexicon for Kannada using Translation and Word Embedding Techniques</b>?</p>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between">
            <button class="m3-button outline-button">cancel</button>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end">
                <button class="m3-button red-button" style="padding-inline: 1.2rem;">delete</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="overlay">
    <div class="dialog">
        <p>Restore <b>KSWN (Kannada SentiWordNet): Developing a Sentiment Lexicon for Kannada using Translation and Word Embedding Techniques</b>?</p>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between">
            <button class="m3-button outline-button">cancel</button>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: flex-end">
                <button class="m3-button purple-button" style="padding-inline: 1rem; box-shadow: none;">restore</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>

<style>
    .yellow-box-buttons {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        margin-left: 1rem;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .yellow-box-buttons button {
        font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.2vw, 0.9rem);
        padding: clamp(0.3rem, 0.8vw, 0.5rem) clamp(0.6rem, 1.5vw, 1rem);
        border-radius: clamp(8px, 2vw, 10rem);
    }

    .text-field input {
        background-color: white;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .yellow-box {
            padding: 1rem !important;
            margin: 0 !important;
        }

        .yellow-box-text {
            font-size: 0.9rem !important;
        }

        .yellow-box-buttons {
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            gap: 0.4rem;
        }

        .yellow-box-buttons button {
            font-size: clamp(0.6rem, 1.8vw, 0.8rem) !important;
            padding: clamp(0.25rem, 0.6vw, 0.4rem) clamp(0.5rem, 1.2vw, 0.8rem) !important;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .yellow-box {
            padding: 0.8rem !important;
        }

        .yellow-box-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem !important;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.2rem !important;
            margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem 1rem !important;
        }

        .authors {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .yellow-box-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column !important;
            gap: 0.3rem;
            margin-left: 0 !important;
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
        }

        .yellow-box-buttons button {
            font-size: clamp(0.5rem, 2.5vw, 0.7rem) !important;
            padding: clamp(0.2rem, 0.5vw, 0.3rem) clamp(0.4rem, 1vw, 0.6rem) !important;
            width: 100% !important;
        }
    }
</style>
</html>